Verb To Be (Simple Present Negative)
===========================
ser/estar

i 	 am	 not happy
you  are not here
he   is	 not amazing
she  is  not beautiful
it   is  not amazing
we   are not here
they are not happy

verb be      --  others verbs
=============================
i am not 	<--> i don't go
You are not <--> you don't speak
He is not 	<--> he doesn't run

Contrações:
==========
i'm not happy
i ain't --> isso é errado!! extremamente informal

you're not here
you aren't here

he's not amazing
he isn't amazing

she's not beautiful
she isn't beautiful

we're not here
we aren't here

they're not happy
they aren't happy

